The Medieval Epic is a 3D game, where your character evolves into a medieval world, looking for a better future. \nYou will have to fight against various enemies, from a simple prison guard, to a tyrannical king, passing by a bear. \nThe Medieval Epic wants to be a game of adventure, fighting, and strategy.
